NAF.raw: http : / / www . vancouverdesi . com / sports / wladimir - klitschko - stops - tony - thompson - in - 6th - round - to - retain - world - heavyweight - titles / 208622 / Wladimir Klitschko stops Tony Thompson in 6th round to retain world heavyweight titles Wladimir Klitschko stopped Tony Thompson in the sixth round to retain his WBA , IBF and WBO heavyweight title belts Saturday night . The 36 - year - old champion Klitschko , 58 - 3 with 51 knockouts , floored Thompson with a big right hand near the end of the fifth round at Stade de Suisse , and the 40 - year - old American never recovered . The Ukrainian champion dropped Thompson again in the sixth , and referee Sam Williams gave the challenger a standing count before stopping the fight . In 2008 , Klitschko stopped Thompson in the 11th round . Thompson , who was the mandatory challenger nominated by the IBF , dropped to 36 - 3 .
